JOB NAME:  IdsClmLnFkey
CALLED BY:  IdsEmrProcedureClmLnLoadSeq
DESCRIPTION:
\(9)Foreign key and code lookup for Claim Line data in 
\(9)preparation for load into IDS table CLM_LN

PRIMARY SOURCE:   .../key/FctsClmLnExtr.FctsClmLn.uniq

